'''薩利姆·加齊·賽義德'''（{{lang-en|Salim Ghazi Saeedi}}，{{bd|1981年|7月19日}}），生於[[伊朗|伊朗]][[德黑蘭|德黑蘭]]，是一名伊朗[[作曲家|作曲家]]和[[結他手|結他手]]

萨利姆是伊朗作曲家、吉他演奏家，其作品涵盖从前卫金属<ref>Windhawk, "[http://www.progarchives.com/album.asp?id=21768 Progarchives.com's review on Ustuqus-al-Uss album] {{Wayback|url=http://www.progarchives.com/album.asp?id=21768 |date=20140731125601 }}", ProgArchives, May 23, 2009</ref>、[[融合爵士樂|融合爵士]]<ref>MP, "[http://www.rezensator.de/saeedi_iconophobic.htm Albumbesprechung Salim Ghazi Saeedi - Iconophobic] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120626032923/http://www.rezensator.de/saeedi_iconophobic.htm |date=2012-06-26 }}, Rezensator.de, 2010</ref>、到前卫派[[室内乐|古典]]<ref name="#1">Lee Henderson, "[http://www.prognaut.com/reviews/salim-ghazi-saeedi.html Iconophobic Album Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.prognaut.com/reviews/salim-ghazi-saeedi.html |date=20130621222100 }}", ProgNaut, October 13, 2010</ref>室内摇滚以及前卫电子摇滚音乐的多种风格。此外，一些评论家更喜欢用艺术摇滚乐来形容他的音乐，将他的音乐视为[[簡約音樂|极简抽象派]]的艺术作品<ref>Steven Reid, "[http://www.seaoftranquility.org/reviews.php?op=showcontent&id=9689 Iconophobic Album Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.seaoftranquility.org/reviews.php?op=showcontent&id=9689 |date=20140407095412 }}", Sea of Tranquility, September 28th 2010</ref>。

評論員曾經將他的音樂與[[麥克·歐菲爾德|麥克·歐菲爾德]]作比較。<ref name="#2">Hard Rock Service, [http://www.rockhard.pl/main/service/salimghazisaeedi/iconophobicrec.html Iconophobic Album Review] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130416102930/http://www.rockhard.pl/main/service/salimghazisaeedi/iconophobicrec.html |date=2013-04-16 }}, Vincent, Jul 2011</ref>

==传记==
一些乐评人将他的音乐与Univers Zero, Art Zoyd<ref>Siggy Zielinski, "[http://www.babyblaue-seiten.de/album_10981.html#oben Iconophobic Album Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.babyblaue-seiten.de/album_10981.html#oben |date=20140407081142 }}", BabyBlaue.de prog-review, 17.10.2010</ref><ref>ProgNaut webzine, Lee Henderson, [http://prognaut.com/reviews/salim-ghazi-saeedi.html Iconophobic Review] {{Wayback|url=http://prognaut.com/reviews/salim-ghazi-saeedi.html |date=20130621222100 }}, Oct 2010</ref><ref>The Rocktologist, Rok Podgrajšek, [http://www.therocktologist.com/ghazi-saeedi-salim---human-encounter.html Human Encounter Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.therocktologist.com/ghazi-saeedi-salim---human-encounter.html |date=20140407085024 }}, Oct 2011</ref>, John Zorn<ref>Digg*, [http://www.digg.be/articles.php?id=3669 Human Encounter Review] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421044206/http://www.digg.be/articles.php?id=3669 |date=2013-04-21 }}, Quincy Cloet, Nov 2011</ref> Patrick O'Hearn, Mike Oldfield<ref name="#2"/>, Djam Karet, Birdsongs of the Mesozoic<ref>"Gary Hill, [http://www.musicstreetjournal.com/index_cdreviews_display.cfm?id=102815 Iconophobic Album Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.musicstreetjournal.com/index_cdreviews_display.cfm?id=102815 |date=20140407084045 }}", Music Street Journal, Issue 85, December 2010</ref>, David Bedford, Richard Pinhas, ZNR, Mecano<ref name="#1"/>, Present, Aranis<ref>Peter van Haerenborgh, "[http://www.progwereld.org/cms/recensies/album/salim-ghazi-saeedi-iconophobic/ Iconophobic Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.progwereld.org/cms/recensies/album/salim-ghazi-saeedi-iconophobic/ |date=20140407084244 }}", Progwereld, Mar 2011</ref>, Dick Dale<ref>Richard Poulin, [http://gnosis2000.net/reviews/arashk.htm Abrahadabra Review] {{Wayback|url=http://gnosis2000.net/reviews/arashk.htm |date=20160303215508 }}, Gnosis2000, May 2008</ref>。Harmonie Magazine将他的吉他演奏同King Crimson中的Robert Fripp相提并论<ref>Philippe Gnana, "[http://www.harmonie-magazine.com/en/allnumeros.php Iconophobic Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.harmonie-magazine.com/en/allnumeros.php |date=20150715153631 }}", ''Harmonie Magazine'', No. 70, Nov 2010, p. 30</ref><ref>Peter van Haerenborgh, [http://www.progwereld.org/cms/recensies/album/salim-ghazi-saeedi-iconophobic/ Iconophobic Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.progwereld.org/cms/recensies/album/salim-ghazi-saeedi-iconophobic/ |date=20140407084244 }}, Progwereld, Mar 2011</ref><ref>Artrock.pl, [http://artrock.pl/recenzje/51271/salim_ghazi_saeedi_iconophobic.html Iconophobic Album Review] {{Wayback|url=http://artrock.pl/recenzje/51271/salim_ghazi_saeedi_iconophobic.html |date=20140407071634 }}, Wojciech Kapała, May 2011</ref><ref>Gary Hill, [http://www.musicstreetjournal.com/index_cdreviews_display.cfm?id=103266 Human Encounter Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.musicstreetjournal.com/index_cdreviews_display.cfm?id=103266 |date=20140407085938 }}, Music Street Journal, Issue 85, Dec 2011</ref>。

他的专辑是概念专辑，借用了古典音乐、电子音乐以及前卫摇滚的元素，并用多种多样的乐器来表现<ref>"The Progressive Rock Files, [http://www.jerrylucky.com/shorttakereviews_004.htm Iconophobic Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jerrylucky.com/shorttakereviews_004.htm |date=20140407085211 }}, Jerry Lucky, Mar 2011</ref>。

